00:00:12.937 --> 00:00:18.290
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:29.079 --> 00:00:33.297
What are you going to cook for us today?
Peni Mixture

00:00:34.968 --> 00:00:37.182
Ingredients required for Peni Mixture

00:00:37.182 --> 00:00:47.462
Fine Vermicelli, Red Gram, Cashew Nuts, Raisins,
 Almonds, Salt, Red Chilli Powder, Garam Masala &amp; Oil

00:00:58.740 --> 00:01:03.243
Heat some oil in a pan for deep fry

00:01:07.489 --> 00:01:21.945
Take some red grams, soak them in water for half hour,
remove them and clean them with a cloth &amp; keep it aside

00:01:47.124 --> 00:01:55.632
Deep fry the soaked red gram in the pan

00:01:58.331 --> 00:02:04.993
Take a bowl, add some fine vermicelli and fried red grams into it 

00:02:05.786 --> 00:02:16.622
Deep fry some cashew nuts, remove
 them &amp; add them into the bowl

00:02:18.582 --> 00:02:24.886
Deep fry some raisins, remove 
them &amp; add them into the bowl

00:02:27.382 --> 00:02:36.410
Deep fry some almonds, remove
 them &amp; add them into the bowl

00:02:39.924 --> 00:02:44.526
Add some red chilli powder into the bowl

00:02:50.565 --> 00:02:55.596
Add some salt into the bowl 

00:03:00.015 --> 00:03:05.053
Add some garam masala into the bowl

00:03:07.563 --> 00:03:14.320
Now mix them well

00:03:18.983 --> 00:03:24.467
Take the Peni Mixture into a serving bowl 

